{"tha-ap115:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap115:0.2":"Mahaparivaravagga ","tha-ap115:0.3":"3 Saranagamaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap115:1.1":"“Ubhinnam devarajunam, ","tha-ap115:1.2":"sangamo samupatthito; ","tha-ap115:1.3":"Ahosi samupabyulho, ","tha-ap115:1.4":"mahaghoso avattatha. ","tha-ap115:2.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap115:2.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap115:2.3":"Antalikkhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap115:2.4":"samvejesi mahajanam. ","tha-ap115:3.1":"Sabbe deva attamana, ","tha-ap115:3.2":"nikkhittakavacavudha; ","tha-ap115:3.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap115:3.4":"ekaggasimsu tavade. ","tha-ap115:4.1":"Mayham sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap115:4.2":"vacasabhimudirayi; ","tha-ap115:4.3":"Anukampako lokavidu, ","tha-ap115:4.4":"nibbapesi mahajanam. ","tha-ap115:5.1":"Padutthacitto manujo, ","tha-ap115:5.2":"ekapanam vihethayam; ","tha-ap115:5.3":"Tena cittappadosena, ","tha-ap115:5.4":"apayam upapajjati. ","tha-ap115:6.1":"Sangamasise nagova, ","tha-ap115:6.2":"bahu pane vihethayam; ","tha-ap115:6.3":"Nibbapetha sakam cittam, ","tha-ap115:6.4":"ma hannittho punappunam. ","tha-ap115:7.1":"Dvinnampi yakkharajunam, ","tha-ap115:7.2":"sena sa vimhita ahu; ","tha-ap115:7.3":"Sarananca upagacchum, ","tha-ap115:7.4":"lokajettham sutadinam. ","tha-ap115:8.1":"Sannapetvana janatam, ","tha-ap115:8.2":"padamuddhari cakkhuma; ","tha-ap115:8.3":"Pekkhamanova devehi, ","tha-ap115:8.4":"pakkami uttaramukho. ","tha-ap115:9.1":"Pathamam saranam gacchim, ","tha-ap115:9.2":"dvipadindassa tadino; ","tha-ap115:9.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap115:9.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap115:10.1":"Mahadundubhinama ca, ","tha-ap115:10.2":"solasasum rathesabha; ","tha-ap115:10.3":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap115:10.4":"rajano cakkavattino. ","tha-ap115:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap115:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap115:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap115:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saranagamaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap115:13.1":"Saranagamaniyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}